{"updated_at": {"date": {"d": "22", "m": "05", "Y": "2026"}, "time": {"H": "07", "M": "34", "S": "00"}}, "news": [{"title": "Water scarcity hits premium townships across Indore", "para": "Indore's upscale colonies are grappling with a severe water crisis as borewells dry up and Narmada supply proves insufficient. Residents are now heavily reliant on costly private water tankers, leading to increased maintenance charges and disrupted daily routines. The situation is expected to worsen as summer temperatures rise.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/infrastructure/water-scarcity-hits-premium-townships-across-indore/131258338?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-231624/131258338.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "infrastructure"}, {"title": "Seven Pune civic body colonies up for redevelopment, residents get notices to vacate", "para": "Pune Municipal Corporation has issued notices to occupants of seven dilapidated housing complexes, urging them to vacate for redevelopment. Approximately 1,900 flats are in poor condition, with 288 prioritized for demolition and rebuilding. The project aims to provide tenants with new 550 sqft properties on a rental basis after reconstruction.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/residential/pune-municipal-corporation-to-redevelop-seven-dilapidated-housing-colonies/131255993?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-89710/131255993.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "residential"}, {"title": "Mumbai: Commercial tower surfaces in DRP plan for Mulund salt pans", "para": "Navbharat Mega Developers, the special purpose vehicle for the Dharavi Redevelopment Project, has submitted a plan to develop Mulund, Bhandup, and Kanjurmarg salt pans. The proposal includes 18 free-sale and one commercial building on Mulund's salt pan, alongside rehabilitation towers.", "href": "https://realty.economictimes.indiatimes.com/news/commercial/mumbais-mulund-salt-pans-controversial-commercial-development-proposed/131255894?utm_source=newslisting&utm_medium=latestNews", "img": "data:image/png;base64, ", "img-src": "https://etimg.etb2bimg.com/thumb/img-size-257644/131255894.cms?width=150&height=112", "tag": "commercial"}]}